      "rationale": "Benchmark problems from ASME V&V 10.1 and NAFEMS LE1/LE10 were reproduced to within 0.5% of analytical solutions. Nonlinear contact patch test confirmed consistent contact force transmission across mesh densities. All code-verification results archived and traceable to solver version identifiers."
