      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement are the three primary QoIs specified in ASTM F1717 and directly relevant to the clinical performance of pedicle screw constructs under compression-bending loading. These quantities map directly to the intended use statement and the regulatory submission QoI requirements identified in the design history file."
