      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level.",
      "rationale": "Validation activity directly replicates the COU: same device design, same loading modality (compression-bending), same standard test method (ASTM F1717), same material system (Ti-6Al-4V ELI), and same prediction objectives. The validation scenario is classified as a direct validation per ASME V&V 40 Table 5.1. No extrapolation from a surrogate geometry or loading condition is required."
